.row
	.col-md-12
		p.lead Finally, add this revision to an edit.

h2 Submit Revision
.row
	.col-md-6.col-md-offset-3.form-horizontal
		.form-group
			label.col-md-3.control-label Revision Note
			.col-md-9
				textarea.form-control(rows='3', data-bind='value: revisionNote')
		.form-group
			.col-md-4.col-md-offset-4
				button.btn.btn-success.btn-block(data-bind='click: submitRevision') Submit
